OL,3,CStudy reveals scale of cyclists and e-
OL,4,Cscooter riders ignoring law in London
OL,6,FSome motorists also behaved badly with
OL,7,F11% distracted at red lights,
OL,8,Fincluding 4% of drivers seen on their
OL,9,Fphones along with other distractions
OL,10,Fincluded eating and drinking as well
OL,11,Fas smoking and vaping while driving.
OL,13,FThe study found Elephant & Castle in
OL,14,FSouth London was among the worst for
OL,15,Fboth running red lights and distracted
OL,16,Fdrivers, while almost no cyclists or e-
OL,17,FScooter riders stopped at the red
OL,18,Flight at Streatham High Road &
OL,19,FGreyhound Lane.
