OL,3,CStudy reveals scale of cyclists and e-
OL,4,Cscooter riders ignoring law in London
OL,6,FBryn Brooker, Head of Road Safety at
OL,7,FNextbase, commented: "Junctions can be
OL,8,Fvery dangerous places and must be
OL,9,Ftreated with respect. It doesn't
OL,10,Fmatter if you're a driver, a cyclist,
OL,11,For on an e-scooter - running the red
OL,12,Flight is illegal and puts you and
OL,13,Fothers in danger. Hitting a pedestrian
OL,14,Fwill be life-changing for both you and
OL,15,Fthe victim, and you could easily be
OL,16,Fhit by traffic coming from another
OL,17,Fdirection. It's just not worth it,
OL,18,Fever.
